sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant DS as DispatcherServlet
    participant HM as HandlerMapping
    participant HA as HandlerAdapter
    participant Handler as @Controller 方法
    participant VR as ViewResolver
    participant View as 视图

    Client->>DS: HTTP 请求
    DS->>DS: doService → doDispatch
    DS->>HM: getHandler(request)
    HM-->>DS: HandlerExecutionChain<br/>(Handler + Interceptors)

    DS->>HA: getHandlerAdapter(handler)
    HA-->>DS: RequestMappingHandlerAdapter

    DS->>HA: handle(request, response, handler)
    HA->>Handler: invoke(参数解析)
    Handler-->>HA: @ResponseBody / ModelAndView

    alt 返回视图名
        HA->>VR: resolveViewName(name)
        VR-->>HA: View 对象
        HA->>View: render()
    else 直接返回数据
        HA-->>DS: 写入 Response Body
    end

    DS-->>Client: HTTP 响应

    Note over DS,View: 三大组件：<br/>HandlerMapping（找 Handler）<br/>HandlerAdapter（执行 Handler）<br/>ViewResolver（解析视图）
